title: IRON FIST S/S'14 LONDON LAUNCH PARTY
description:
To launch our Spring/Summer collection landing in the UK, we decided to take over one of Soho's premiere clubs for one night only...
Some of our favorite UK hotties came down to do DJ sets, including While She Sleeps, Alexis Knox, Bury Tomorrow, Rise To Remain & The Skints. 
With a room filled with babes, bands & a HELLA load of booze the outcome was obviously the wildest night London has seen in a long time, and guess what...we caught the whole thing on film.
Keep your eyes peeled for the next IF UK party coming SUMMER 2014. BIGGER, BETTER & BOOZIER.
